title: Dell Latitude 5430: Release date, price, and everything you need to know
content:
Dell recently announced a refreshed lineup of Latitude laptops, all featuring Intel 12th-generation processors, among other upgrades. Among the new devices, there’s the Dell Latitude 5430, a new 14-inch business laptop geared towards the more mainstream crowd.
